<h2>Itching or burning, Pain or discomfort and Swelling</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms itching or burning, pain or discomfort and swelling including Urinary tract infection (UTI), Lice, and Cellulitis.</p>
<p>There  are 7 conditions  associated with itching or burning, pain or discomfort and swelling. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
<div class="related_conditions">
<ul class="results_list">
