</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7c16&amp;bpid[0]=35&amp;sid[0]=129&amp;bpid[1]=35&amp;sid[1]=1&amp;bpid[2]=35&amp;sid[2]=5" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Lice</a><p>Head lice are tiny visible insects that infest the hair and scalp causing itchiness and bumps in that area.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7ac1&amp;bpid[0]=35&amp;sid[0]=129&amp;bpid[1]=35&amp;sid[1]=1&amp;bpid[2]=35&amp;sid[2]=5" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Cellulitis</a><p>Cellulitis, a bacterial infection of the skin, causes red, tender skin that is usually swollen and warm. </p>
</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e8109&amp;bpid[0]=35&amp;sid[0]=129&amp;bpid[1]=35&amp;sid[1]=1&amp;bpid[2]=35&amp;sid[2]=5" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Crabs</a><p>Crabs, or pubic lice, are tiny, six-legged insects that infest pubic skin and hair and cause intense itching.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e80d7&amp;bpid[0]=35&amp;sid[0]=129&amp;bpid[1]=35&amp;sid[1]=1&amp;bpid[2]=35&amp;sid[2]=5" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Chemical burns</a><p>A chemical burn can cause symptoms ranging from burning and blisters to pain and shortness of breath.</p>
</li>
